Germany Says Portugal ‘Is on the Right Path’ With ‘Reforms’

-- B y   L e o n   M a n g a s a r i a n
-- 
2011-10-14T09:49:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/germany-says-portugal-is-on-the-right-path-with-reforms-.html
German government spokesman Steffen
Seibert said  Portugal  “is on the right path” with its
“reforms.”  “The German government is observing with great respect how
the Portuguese government and people are following reforms,”
Seibert said today to reporters in Berlin.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Leon Mangasarian at 
 lmangasarian@bloomberg.net  